# WP-INFRA-IO-002 — reduce Cursor indexing / watcher I/O on VPS and dev hosts.
# See docs/ops/WP-INFRA-IO-002-VPS-IO-Guardrails.md

# Node / Next.js
**/node_modules/
**/.next/
**/.turbo/
**/.cache/
**/coverage/
**/dist/
**/build/

# Python
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/*.pyd

# Runtime / logs
**/logs/
**/tmp/
**/*.log

# Git internals (large object store)
**/.git/objects/
**/.git/subtree-cache/

# Local sync / exports
**/data/sync/
